'''Deep Ear''' was a faction of the [[Bothan Spynet/Legends|Bothan Spynet]] led by [[Borsk Fey'lya]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The group came into possession of the [[Death Star II/Legends|Death Star II]] plans on the ''[[Suprosa]]'' and fled to the planet [[Gellefon]]. While on this planet, most of the members were captured by [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Schennt]] and then soon freed by a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] who were called to help by [[Jade (mercenary)|Watcher]]. They then went on to give the plans to [[Alliance High Command/Legends|Alliance High Command]] at [[Keff Base]] in the [[Sullust system/Legends|Sullust system]].

==Behind the scenes==
The name of the group Deep Ear is an obvious reference to [[Wikipedia:Deep Throat|Deep Throat]], the codename of the source that exposed the [[Wikipedia:Watergate|Watergate scandal]].

